The paper also mentions the use of neural networks for approximation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of these models in computer vision, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions the number of free parameters in the models, which is a common topic in neural network optimization, suggesting that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
